{"tid":387916,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[單親媽溺斃]痛失好媽媽 19歲女崩潰：好後悔冇盡囡嘅責任","createTime":"2017-09-05T04:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T09:32:17.000Z","uid":34498,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30ef25873cfcba30140a0d76cb78443a53cb613f","tid":387916,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/iq57spfz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fiq57spfz&h=e9089e76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「佢臨返工前都會游水，但今日出咗去就冇返過嚟！」42歲姓林女子上午於屯門蝴蝶灣泳灘溺斃，遺下現正就讀副學士課程的19歲姓馮獨女，陰陽相隔，女兒接受《蘋果》訪問時崩潰痛哭：「好掛住佢...」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者的丈夫6年前因糖尿病併發逝世，自始母兼父職，任機場保安員養家，獨力養大女兒。死者熱愛游泳，每日返工前必會到海灘游早水，惟今晨卻不幸遇溺，一去不返。愛女痛失雙親，孤苦無依，就連母親的殮葬費亦成問題，她回憶起母親多年來克勤克儉，為她供書教學，不禁自責：「佢好錫我，好想帶佢食好嘢，好後悔冇盡囡嘅責任！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20150717/53985378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20150717%2F53985378&d=eD48OVMchSvo1iK61qzxjvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=2fcd382b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20150717%2F53985378&h=a978f01c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20150717/53985378</a>"},{"pid":"a9a3cf49d6936ea83e83755bfa3331098c42925f","tid":387916,"uid":44333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"20150717"},{"pid":"b14af81a207cd948e55e2b427cf1d60317c86dc7","tid":387916,"uid":73,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:57:19.000Z","msg":"有冇清朝新聞睇下?<br />\n想考古"},{"pid":"4eb27bb69a5620e0648f39a8d59633bf62cf14d8","tid":387916,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c972469d65962874b48b5fa79f549a2bab6677","tid":387916,"uid":29702,"like":0,"d